  +pppconfig-2.3.21.ebuild:
  Version bump. Use mirror:// (bug #413341). Rewrite LINGUAS support using
  strip-linguas (maybe bug #403633).

  12 Nov 2007; Alin Năstac <mrness@gentoo.org> -pppconfig-2.3.15.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

